        </div>
        <div class="homePage__navbarRight">
          <button class="sign-in">Sign in</button>
          <button class="sign-up">Sign up</button>
        </div>
      </nav>
      <div class="homePage__body">
        <div class="homePage__bodyLeft">
          <h1>High-quality videoconferencing, now available to everyone</h1>
          <p>
            We have adapted Meeteor, our videoconferencing service pprofessional
            secure, in order to make it available to everyone.
          </p>
          <form action="" id="link-form">
            <button class="redBtn" id="new-meeting">
              <span class="material-icons"> video_call </span>
              <p>New meeting</p>
            </button>
            <span class="meetUrl">
